b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Article Forge is best suited for bulk article generation, PBN content, automated blogging, SEO content, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Rytr, meanwhile, shines for budget conscious writers, short copy, emails, social media, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2015, Article Forge describes itself as \"Fully automated AI article generation in one click.\" Rytr, established in 2021, positions itself as \"Budget-friendly AI writing assistant with 40+ use cases.\" With 6 years between them, Article Forge brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Rytr offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Rytr** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (6.0 vs 4.0), more features (9 vs 4), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Article Forge is a poor choice — far from it. Article Forge excels in its own right, particularly for bulk article generation and PBN content.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value very affordable with unlimited plan at $9/mo, go with Rytr. If fully automated one-click article generation matters more to you, Article Forge is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
